Test Plan 
- strategy that will be used to test an application,
- the resources that will be used, 
- the test environment in which testing will be performed, 
- limitations of the testing 
- the schedule of the testing activities

Test Scenario
-several steps
-notifies what area in the application will be tested

Test Case
-single steps

Traceability Matrix
- table that is used to trace the requirements during the SDLC
- inked with its associated test case so that testing can be done as per the mentioned requirements

